hopobject.body: Can I call you back? betamethasone 1 ointment170 The hybrid powertrain gives CO2 emissions of 103g/km, which is 6g/km less than a BMW 320D Efficient Dynamics auto. That's a plus point for anyone that runs one as a company car, although the IS can't quite match its German rivals' Combined fuel economy, with a figure of 64.2mpg to the BMW's 68.9mpg. Real-world fuel economy isn't likely to be as impressive - I averaged about 47mg over nearly 500 miles, on a mix of city, motorway and country roads.
